## 1. Pre-Migration Requirements

- [ ] **Complete PatternFly 5 upgrade first** — Ensure your product is fully on PF5 before migrating to PF6
- [ ] **Ensure Node.js >= 10** is installed (for codemods)
- [ ] **Create a clean git branch** for migration work
- [ ] **Run codemods BEFORE any manual changes** — Manual changes first will cause codemod conflicts

---

## 2. Package Upgrades

Update all `@patternfly/*` packages from v5 to v6. This must be done **manually before running codemods**.

| Package | Action |
|---------|--------|
| `@patternfly/react-core` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-icons` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-table` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-charts` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-tokens` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-styles` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-topology` | Upgrade to v6 (if used) |
| `@patternfly/react-code-editor` | Upgrade to v6 (if used) |
| `@patternfly/react-log-viewer` | Upgrade to v6 (if used) |
| `@patternfly/react-catalog-view-extension` | Upgrade to v6 (if used) |
| `@patternfly/react-component-groups` | Upgrade to v6 (if used) |
| `@patternfly/react-user-feedback` | Upgrade to v6 (if used) |
| `victory` / `victory-core` / `victory-tooltip` | **NEW peer dependency** — install if using charts |

### Charts Peer Dependencies (NEW)
Victory is now an **optional peer dependency** for `@patternfly/react-charts`. Install either:
- `victory` (single package for all features), OR
- Specific packages: `victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`, `victory-area`, etc.

---

## 3. Codemods — Automated Migration Tools

Run these in order:

### Step 1: Main codemods
```bash
# Dry run first (shows issues without fixing)
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6

# Fix automatically
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --fix

# For large codebases
NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096 npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --fix
```

### Step 2: Clean up data-codemods attributes
```bash
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --only data-codemods-cleanup --fix
```

### Step 3: Class name updater (CSS class prefixes `pf-v5` → `pf-v6`)
```bash
npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <path-to-src> --v6 --fix
```

### Step 4: CSS vars updater (for `.css`, `.scss`, `.less`, `.md` files)
```bash
npx @patternfly/css-vars-updater <path-to-src> --fix
# Or interactive mode for finer control:
npx @patternfly/css-vars-updater <path-to-src> -i
```

### Step 5: Tokens update (React tokens in `.js`/`.tsx` files)
The main codemods include a `tokens-update` rule that:
- Auto-fixes global non-color tokens
- Replaces global color tokens with `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink) for manual replacement
- Flags component/chart tokens for manual update

---

## 4. Component Replacements

### Components Renamed

| Old Component | New Component | Codemod Rule | Notes |
|--------------|---------------|--------------|-------|
| `Text` | `Content` | `text-replace-with-content` | Auto-fixable |
| `TextContent` | `Content` | `text-replace-with-content` | Auto-fixable |
| `TextList` | `Content` with `component` prop | `text-replace-with-content` | Auto-fixable |
| `TextListItem` | `Content` with `component` prop | `text-replace-with-content` | Auto-fixable |
| `MastheadBrand` (old) | `MastheadLogo` | `masthead-name-changes` | Auto-fixable |
| `MastheadBrand` (new) | New wrapper component | `masthead-structure-changes` | Wraps MastheadLogo |
| `ToolbarChipGroupContent` | `ToolbarLabelGroupContent` | `toolbarChipGroupContent-rename-component` | Auto-fixable |
| `NotAuthorized` | `UnauthorizedAccess` | Component groups codemod | Auto-fixable |
| `InvalidObject` | `MissingPage` | Component groups codemod | Auto-fixable |
| `ContentHeader` | `PageHeader` | Component groups codemod | Auto-fixable |

### Components Deprecated (moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`)

| Component | Replacement | Codemod Rule |
|-----------|-------------|--------------|
| `Chip` | `Label` (with `variant="outline"`) | `chip-replace-with-label` |
| `ChipGroup` | `LabelGroup` | `chip-replace-with-label` |
| `Tile` | `Card` | `tile-deprecated` |
| `Modal` (old API) | `Modal` (new promoted API from Next) | `modal-deprecated` / `modalNext-promoted` |
| `DualListSelector` (old) | `DualListSelector` (Next promoted) | `dualListSelector-deprecated` / `dualListSelectorNext-promoted` |
| `DragDrop` (old) | New drag-and-drop implementation | `dragDrop-deprecated` |

### Components Fully Removed (no deprecated path)

| Removed Component | Recommended Replacement |
|-------------------|------------------------|
| `ApplicationLauncher` | Custom menu with `Menu`/`MenuToggle`/`Popper` |
| `ContextSelector` | Custom menu with `Menu`/`MenuToggle`/`Popper` |
| `Dropdown` (deprecated/old) | Composable `Dropdown` or template `Dropdown` |
| `OptionsMenu` | Composable `Select` or template `Select` |
| `PageHeader` | `Masthead` + `Toolbar` |
| `Select` (deprecated/old) | Composable `Select` or template `Select` |
| `PageNavigation` | Removed entirely |
| `KebabToggle` | `MenuToggle` with `variant="plain"` |
| `EmptyStateHeader` | Now internal to `EmptyState` (use props) |
| `EmptyStateIcon` | Now internal to `EmptyState` (use `icon` prop) |

---

## 5. Component API Changes

### Accordion
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `AccordionContent` `isHidden` prop | **Removed** — visibility now auto-set by `AccordionItem`'s `isExpanded` | `accordionContent-remove-isHidden-prop` |
| `AccordionToggle` `isExpanded` prop | **Moved** to `AccordionItem` | `accordionToggle-move-isExpanded-prop` |
| `AccordionItem` markup | Now renders a wrapper `div` element | Warning only |

### Avatar
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `border` prop | **Replaced** with `isBordered` | `avatar-replace-border-for-isBordered` |

### Banner
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `variant` prop | **Removed** — use `color` or `status` instead | `banner-replace-variantProp` |
| `color` values | `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"` | `colorProps-replaced-colors` |

### Button
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `isActive` prop | **Renamed** to `isClicked` | `button-rename-isActive` |
| Icon children | Icons must be passed via `icon` prop, not as children (for `variant="plain"`) | `button-moveIcons-icon-prop` |
| `isDisabled` behavior | Now sets `disabled` attr, NOT `aria-disabled` (except when `component` is not "button") | Manual |
| Text wrapping | Button text now wrapped in a `<span class="pf-v6-c-button__text">` | Test impact |

### Card
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `isSelectableRaised` | **Removed** | `card-remove-various-props` |
| `isDisabledRaised` | **Removed** | `card-remove-various-props` |
