## 6. Removed/Deprecated Components

### Fully Removed (no codemod fix, manual migration required)

- **ApplicationLauncher** → Use custom menu pattern with `Menu`/`MenuToggle`/`Popper`
- **ContextSelector** → Use custom menu pattern
- **Dropdown** (deprecated/legacy) → Use composable `Dropdown`
- **OptionsMenu** → Use composable `Select`
- **PageHeader** → Use `Masthead` + `Toolbar`
- **Select** (deprecated/legacy) → Use composable `Select`
- **KebabToggle** → Use `MenuToggle` with `variant="plain"`
- **PageNavigation** → Component removed entirely

---

## 7. Import Path Changes

### Chart Imports (CRITICAL)
```typescript
// OLD (PF5)
import { Chart, ChartArea, ChartBar, ... } from '@patternfly/react-charts';

// NEW (PF6) — all Victory-based charts move to /victory subpath
import { Chart, ChartArea, ChartBar, ... } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory';
```
**Codemod:** `chartsImport-moved` — Auto-fixable

### Modal Imports
```typescript
// OLD (PF5) — old Modal moved to deprecated
import { Modal, ModalVariant } from '@patternfly/react-core';
// Becomes:
import { Modal, ModalVariant } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';

// NEW promoted Modal (was ModalNext)
import { Modal, ModalBody, ModalHeader, ModalFooter } from '@patternfly/react-core';
```

### Deprecated Component Imports
```typescript
// Components moved to /deprecated path:
import { Chip, ChipGroup } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';
import { Tile } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';
import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';  // old Modal
import { DragDrop, Draggable, Droppable } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';
import { DualListSelector } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';  // old
```

### Text → Content Import
```typescript
// OLD
import { Text, TextContent, TextList, TextListItem, TextVariants } from '@patternfly/react-core';

// NEW
import { Content, ContentVariants } from '@patternfly/react-core';
```

### React Tokens Import Path
```typescript
// Token names changed from camelCase to underscore-prefixed format:
// OLD
import global_FontSize_lg from '@patternfly/react-tokens/dist/esm/global_FontSize_lg';

// NEW
import { t_global_font_size_lg } from '@patternfly/react-tokens';
```

### Log Viewer Styles
```typescript
// OLD
import '@patternfly/react-log-viewer/dist/css/react-log-viewer.css';

// NEW — internal SCSS refactored to CSS
// Check updated import path from react-log-viewer package
```

### User Feedback Styles
```typescript
// NEW — must import CSS file
import '@patternfly/react-user-feedback/dist/esm/Feedback/Feedback.css';
```

---

## 8. CSS/Token/Variable Changes

### CSS Class Prefix Change
```
pf-v5-c-*  →  pf-v6-c-*   (components)
pf-v5-l-*  →  pf-v6-l-*   (layouts)
pf-v5-u-*  →  pf-v6-u-*   (utilities)
```
**Tool:** `@patternfly/class-name-updater --v6`

### CSS Variable / Design Token Overhaul

PF6 introduces a completely new **design token system**. The variable naming convention has fundamentally changed:

#### Global Variable Format Change
```css
/* OLD (PF5) */
--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg
--pf-v5-global--spacer--md
--pf-v5-global--Color--100
--pf-v5-global--BorderRadius--lg
--pf-v5-global--BackgroundColor--200

/* NEW (PF6) */
--pf-t--global--font--size--lg
--pf-t--global--spacer--md
--pf-t--global--text--color--regular     /* colors have no 1:1 mapping */
--pf-t--global--border--radius--large
--pf-t--global--background--color--secondary  /* colors have no 1:1 mapping */
```

#### Component Variable Format Change
```css
/* OLD (PF5) */
--pf-v5-c-about-modal-box--Height
--pf-v5-c-alert--BoxShadow
--pf-v5-c-about-modal-box__brand--PaddingLeft

/* NEW (PF6) */
--pf-v6-c-about-modal-box--Height
--pf-v6-c-alert--BoxShadow
--pf-v6-c-about-modal-box__brand--PaddingInlineStart  /* directional → logical */
```

#### React Token Format Change
```typescript
// OLD
global_FontSize_lg          → t_global_font_size_lg
global_Color_100            → t_temp_dev_tbd  // must manually replace
global_link_Color_hover     → t_global_color_nonstatus_green_clicked  // example

// NEW prefix: all tokens with --pf-t-- value use t_ prefix
// e.g. color_green_10 → t_color_green_10
```

#### Directional Properties → Logical Properties
```css
/* OLD */
PaddingLeft   → PaddingInlineStart
PaddingRight  → PaddingInlineEnd
PaddingTop    → PaddingBlockStart
PaddingBottom → PaddingBlockEnd
MarginLeft    → MarginInlineStart
/* etc. */
```

#### Key Resources for Token Mapping
- [Removed variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [Added variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)
- [PF6 token documentation](https://www.patternfly.org/tokens/all-patternfly-tokens)

### ⚠️ CRITICAL: Color Token Manual Migration
- **No 1:1 mapping** exists for most PF5 color variables to PF6 tokens
- Codemods replace color vars with `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink) to make them visually obvious
- React token equivalent: `t_temp_dev_tbd`
- **You MUST manually replace** every `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` with appropriate PF6 token
- Recommendation: **Remove all CSS overrides first**, then only re-add what's necessary using new tokens

---

## 9. Chart-Specific Changes

### Import Path Migration
```typescript
// ALL Victory-based chart imports must change:
// OLD
import { Chart, ChartArea, ChartAxis, ChartBar, ChartDonut, ... } from '@patternfly/react-charts';

// NEW
import { Chart, ChartArea, ChartAxis, ChartBar, ChartDonut, ... } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory';
```

### Victory Peer Dependencies
Victory is now an **optional peer dependency**. You must install it yourself:
```bash
# Option A: Install all Victory features
npm install victory

# Option B: Install specific packages
npm install victory-core victory-tooltip victory-chart
```

### Chart Token Changes
- Chart-specific tokens (`--pf-v5-chart--*`) need manual replacement
- The codemods' `tokens-update` rule does NOT auto-fix chart tokens
- Check [PF6 token docs](https://www.patternfly.org/tokens/all-patternfly-tokens) for chart token equivalents

---

## 10. Icon Changes

### Icon Prop on Button
Icons are no longer passed as children for plain buttons. Use the `icon` prop:
```tsx
// OLD
<Button variant="plain"><TimesIcon /></Button>

// NEW
<Button variant="plain" icon={<TimesIcon />} />
```

### PageToggleButton
```tsx
// OLD — passing BarsIcon as child
<PageToggleButton><BarsIcon /></PageToggleButton>

// NEW — use isHamburgerButton prop
<PageToggleButton isHamburgerButton />
```

### EmptyState Icons
Icons in EmptyState are now passed via props, not as separate components:
```tsx
// OLD
<EmptyState>
  <EmptyStateHeader icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={CubesIcon} />} titleText="Title" headingLevel="h2" />
</EmptyState>

// NEW
<EmptyState headingLevel="h2" titleText="Title" icon={CubesIcon}>
  <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>
```

---

## 11. Layout/Spacing Changes

### Toolbar Spacing
```tsx
// OLD — spacer/spaceItems props
<ToolbarGroup spacer={{ default: "spacerNone", md: "spacerSm" }} spaceItems={{ default: "spaceItemsMd" }}>

// NEW — gap/columnGap/rowGap props
<ToolbarGroup gap={{ default: "gapNone", md: "gapSm" }}>
```

### Toolbar Alignment
```tsx
// OLD
<ToolbarGroup align={{ default: "alignRight" }}>

// NEW
<ToolbarGroup align={{ default: "alignEnd" }}>
```

### Content/Text Component
The `Text`, `TextContent`, `TextList`, `TextListItem` components are all replaced by a single `Content` component:
```tsx
// OLD
<TextContent>
  <Text component="h1">Title</Text>
  <Text component="p">Paragraph</Text>
  <TextList>
    <TextListItem>Item</TextListItem>
  </TextList>
</TextContent>

// NEW
<Content>
  <Content component="h1">Title</Content>
  <Content component="p">Paragraph</Content>
  <Content component="ul">
    <Content component="li">Item</Content>
  </Content>
</Content>
```

---

## 12. Theme/Dark Mode Changes

### Theming No Longer React-Side
- `backgroundColor` prop **removed** from `Masthead`
- `theme` prop **removed** from `Nav` and `PageSidebar`
- `variant` prop values `"dark"`, `"light"`, `"darker"` **removed** from `PageSection`
- `variant="light300"` **removed** from `Tabs`
- Theming is now handled via CSS tokens/design tokens, not React props

### Dark Mode / Color Scheme
- PF6 uses CSS-native `prefers-color-scheme` and design tokens for theming
- The `<meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">` approach is used
- Products should NOT override theme colors via React props

---

## 13. Breakpoint Changes

PF6 uses **rem units** instead of pixels for breakpoint tokens:

| Breakpoint | Token | Old (px) | New (rem) |
|-----------|-------|----------|-----------|
| xs | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xs` | 0px | 0rem |
| sm | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--sm` | 576px | 36rem |
| md | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--md` | 768px | 48rem |
| lg | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--lg` | 992px | 62rem |
| xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xl` | 1200px | 75rem |
| 2xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--2xl` | 1450px | 90.625rem |

**Action:** If you have pixel-based breakpoint logic in JavaScript, update to rem values (divide px by 16).

---

## 14. Test Impact & Fixes

### Button Tests
1. **`aria-disabled` no longer rendered on buttons:**
   - `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attribute, NOT `aria-disabled`
   - Exception: when `component` prop is NOT "button"
   - `aria-disabled` only renders when `true`
   - **Fix:** Remove tests looking for `aria-disabled` on standard buttons

2. **`byText` queries may break:**
   - Button text is now wrapped in `<span class="pf-v6-c-button__text">`
   - `byText` returns the span, not the button element
   - **Fix:** Use `byRole('button', { name: 'Button text' })` instead

### Select Tests
1. **`byRole` can't find menu options after selection:**
   - Popper menu may be `aria-disabled` after selection
   - **Fix:** Pass `{ hidden: true }` option to query, or set `appendTo="inline"`

### Snapshot Tests
- All CSS class names changed (`pf-v5-*` → `pf-v6-*`)
- Many component DOM structures changed
- **Action:** Regenerate all snapshots after migration

### OUIA Attributes
- OUIA component type prefixes changed: `PF5/` → `PF6/` (e.g., `PF6/Button`, `PF6/Alert`)

---

## 15. Other Breaking Changes

### TypeScript Changes
| Change | Details |
|--------|---------|
| `TextVariants` | Renamed to `ContentVariants` |
| `TextListVariants` | Merged into `ContentVariants` |
| `TextListItemVariants` | Merged into `ContentVariants` |
| `TextProps` | Renamed to `ContentProps` |
| `SplitButtonOptions` interface | **Deleted** |
| `PageSectionVariants` | Only accepts `"default"` or `"secondary"` |
| `DrawerColorVariant.light200` | Replaced with `DrawerColorVariant.secondary` |
| `ToolbarGroupVariant` values | `"button-group"` → `"action-group"`, `"icon-button-group"` → `"action-group-plain"` |
| Toolbar interfaces | Multiple renamed (Chip→Label naming) |
| `WizardStep` `body` prop | No longer accepts `null` |
| `FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` | Renamed |

### Component Groups (`@patternfly/react-component-groups`)
| Change | Codemod |
|--------|---------|
| `LogSnippet` `leftBorderVariant` renamed | `componentGroups-logSnippet-rename-leftBorderVariant` |
| `ErrorState` props renamed | `componentGroups-errorState-rename-props` |
| `MultiContentCard` props removed | `component-groups-multi-content-card-remove-props` |
| `NotAuthorized` → `UnauthorizedAccess` | `component-groups-notAuthorized-rename-to-unauthorizedAccess` |
| `InvalidObject` → `MissingPage` | `component-groups-invalidObject-rename-to-missingPage` |
| `ContentHeader` → `PageHeader` | `component-groups-contentHeader-rename-to-pageHeader` |
| `UnavailableContent` `bodyText` prop updated | `component-groups-unavailableContent-bodyText-props-update` |
| `UnavailableContent` props renamed | `component-groups-unavailable-content-rename-props` |
| `NotAuthorized` props renamed | `component-groups-notAuthorized-rename-props` |
| `InvalidObject` props renamed | `component-groups-invalidObject-rename-props` |
| `InvalidObjectProps` → `MissingPageProps` | `component-groups-invalidObjectProps-rename-to-missingPageProps` |

### Animations
- `enable-animations` codemod: Animations may need to be re-enabled

### Popper Default Change
- `appendTo` default is now `document.body` for Dropdown, Select, and Popper
- This may affect positioning in modals or constrained containers

---

## Migration Execution Order

1. ✅ Update all `@patternfly/*` packages to v6 in `package.json`
2. ✅ Install Victory peer dependencies if using charts
3. ✅ Run `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6` (dry run)
4. ✅ Run `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --fix`
5. ✅ Run `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --only data-codemods-cleanup --fix`
6. ✅ Run `npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <src> --v6 --fix`
7. ✅ Run `npx @patternfly/css-vars-updater <src> --fix`
8. ✅ Build and address remaining errors
9. ✅ Re-run codemods multiple times until no new issues found
10. ✅ Remove all CSS overrides, re-evaluate which are needed
11. ✅ Manually replace all `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` hot pink placeholders
12. ✅ Update pixel-based breakpoint logic to rem values
13. ✅ Fix manually flagged issues (EmptyState, removed components, etc.)
14. ✅ Regenerate test snapshots
15. ✅ Fix failing unit tests (Button `aria-disabled`, `byText` queries, etc.)
16. ✅ Run `make build-frontend` and `make test-frontend`
17. ✅ Visual review of all pages for UI regressions



