<details id="detail-packages">
  <summary>📦 Package Upgrades <span class="tie-tag">TIE</span></summary>
  <div class="detail-content">
    <h4>What Changed in PF6</h4>
    <p>All <code>@patternfly/*</code> packages must be updated to v6. Victory is now a peer dependency for charts.</p>
    
    <h4>Baseline State (main branch)</h4>
    <pre><code>@patternfly/react-core: ^6.4.1
@patternfly/react-icons: ^6.4.0
@patternfly/react-topology: ^6.3.0</code></pre>
    <p>The <code>main</code> branch already has PatternFly 6 packages installed. Neither migration branch needed to change <code>package.json</code>.</p>
    
    <table>
      <tr><th>Aspect</th><th>pf-codemods</th><th>semver/goose</th></tr>
      <tr><td>package.json changed?</td><td>No</td><td>No</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Correct behavior?</td><td>Yes — already on PF6</td><td>Yes — already on PF6</td></tr>
