<!-- Button Icon Prop -->
<details id="detail-button">
  <summary>🔘 Button Icon Prop Migration <span class="winner-tag">semver/goose WINS</span></summary>
  <div class="detail-content">
    <h4>What Changed in PF6</h4>
    <p>In PatternFly 6, icon-only buttons must pass icons via the <code>icon</code> prop instead of as children. The <code>Icon</code> wrapper component is no longer needed for this pattern.
    (<a href="https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade/">PF6 Upgrade Guide</a> — <code>button-moveIcons-icon-prop</code> codemod)</p>
    
    <h4>Before (PF5 pattern on main)</h4>
    <pre><code>&lt;Button variant="plain" isInline&gt;
  &lt;Icon isInline size="sm"&gt;
    &lt;OutlinedQuestionCircleIcon /&gt;
  &lt;/Icon&gt;
&lt;/Button&gt;</code></pre>
    
    <h4>After — pf-codemods branch</h4>
    <pre><code>&lt;Button icon={&lt;Icon isInline size="sm"&gt;
    &lt;OutlinedQuestionCircleIcon /&gt;
  &lt;/Icon&gt;} variant="plain" isInline /&gt;
// Note: Icon wrapper preserved, awkward formatting</code></pre>
    
    <h4>After — semver/goose branch</h4>
    <pre><code>&lt;Button variant="plain" isInline icon={&lt;OutlinedQuestionCircleIcon /&gt;} /&gt;
// Note: Icon wrapper removed, import cleaned up, clean self-closing</code></pre>
    
    <table>
      <tr><th>Aspect</th><th>pf-codemods</th><th>semver/goose</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Files fixed</td><td>3 (HelpPopover, Korrel8rPanel, Popover)</td><td>3 (HelpPopover, Korrel8rPanel, Popover)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Icon wrapper removed?</td><td class="metric-bad">No — Icon component still imported and used</td><td class="metric-good">Yes — cleanly removed</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Self-closing buttons?</td><td class="metric-bad">Partially — Korrel8rPanel has empty body</td><td class="metric-good">Yes — all 3 self-closing</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Unused import removed?</td><td class="metric-bad">No</td><td class="metric-good">Yes (<code>Icon</code> removed from imports)</td></tr>
